name: GSRX Industries
short_description: GSRX Industries Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in acquiring, developing, and operating retail cannabis dispensaries.
long_description: GSRX Industries Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in acquiring, developing, and operating retail cannabis dispensaries. It also engages in the extraction, manufacture, distribution, and delivery of cannabis and cannabinoid products. As of July 16, 2019, the company operated five cannabis dispensaries under the Green Spirit RX name in Puerto Rico; a dispensary under The Green Room name in California; and five pre-qualified locations in Puerto Rico. It also owns and operates GetPureAndNatural.com, an e-commerce site, which offers a range of hemp extract products. The company was formerly known as Green Spirit Industries Inc. and changed its name to GSRX Industries Inc. in July 2018. GSRX Industries Inc. is headquartered in Dorado, Puerto Rico.
